  </div>
  <div class="pr-wrap" style="margin-top:3rem"><h3 class="pr-subh">Meet the team</h3>${teamGrid}</div>
</section>

<!-- 4 · Our expertise -->
<section class="pr-sec">
  <div class="pr-wrap">
    ${kicker("Our expertise")}
    <h2>Built for a service-led pharmacy site.</h2>
    <div class="pr-exp">
      <div class="pr-expcard"><span class="pr-expnum">01</span><h3>Website design &amp; development</h3><p>Strategy, design and build of fast, modern sites, with the Tap brand carried through every page.</p></div>
      <div class="pr-expcard"><span class="pr-expnum">02</span><h3>Booking &amp; service platforms</h3><p>Clear, simple booking for vaccinations, health checks, weight management and more, off the shelf or bespoke.</p></div>
