      <div class="pr-spec__col"><h4>Industry specialism</h4><p>Healthcare &amp; medical, from consultants and clinics to care organisations, alongside retail, hospitality and charity.</p></div>
      <div class="pr-spec__col"><h4>How we work</h4><p>Award-winning design and development in-house, certified across Google and Meta's platforms. The people who strategise are the people who ship.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="pr-band"><img src="/images/office/office-work-01.jpg" alt="Inside the Rooftop Twenty Two studio" loading="lazy"/></div>

<!-- 5 · Our thinking for your site -->
<section class="pr-sec pr-sec--alt">
  <div class="pr-wrap pr-narrow">
    ${kicker("Our thinking for your site")}
    <h2>What the new site should do.</h2>
    ${list([
      "Move off e-commerce to a service and information platform. The site becomes a customer service tool that works 24/7.",
