        <div class="pr-node"><b>Our pharmacies</b><ul><li>A page per location</li><li>Hours &amp; address</li><li>Photos &amp; map</li></ul></div>
        <div class="pr-node pr-node--leaf"><b>Book an appointment</b></div>
        <div class="pr-node pr-node--leaf"><b>Health advice &amp; news</b></div>
        <div class="pr-node pr-node--leaf"><b>Contact</b></div>
        <div class="pr-node pr-node--leaf"><b>Careers</b></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="pr-soft">For discussion. We will confirm the final structure together.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 7 · Booking engine -->
<section class="pr-sec">
  <div class="pr-wrap">
    ${kicker("The booking engine")}
    <h2>Bespoke vs off the shelf.</h2>
    <p class="pr-lead">Booking is the heart of the new site. The right choice depends on how much control you want and how it connects to your other systems.</p>
    <div class="pr-tablewrap"><table class="pr-table">
      <thead><tr><th></th><th>Off the shelf</th><th>Bespoke</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><th>What it is</th><td>A proven tool (Acuity or Bookly) styled to your brand.</td><td>A system we build around your services and five locations.</td></tr>
