        <tr><th>Maps &amp; location finder</th><td>Helps people find and route to their nearest pharmacy.</td><td><span class="pr-tag pr-tag--core">Core</span></td></tr>
        <tr><th>Analytics &amp; tracking</th><td>GA4 and conversion tracking, so we see bookings and improve.</td><td><span class="pr-tag pr-tag--core">Core</span></td></tr>
